WEBVTT


00:01:08.360 --> 00:01:10.120
{\an8}How was that even a breakup, Ms. Lin?

00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:13.200
{\an8}She lied to you so much,
and you're still going on a trip with her?

00:01:13.280 --> 00:01:15.000
{\an8}Since I started dating Ing,

00:01:15.080 --> 00:01:19.200
{\an8}it's felt like a dream, Jane.
I've been really happy.

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:20.440
{\an8}I'll resign, Mr. Pao.

00:01:21.760 --> 00:01:23.760
{\an8}Did you order Play Park
to be shut down, Dad?

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:27.200
{\an8}I've helped you through a difficult time.

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:32.000
{\an8}Now let's move forward with the tutoring,
without worrying about anyone else.

00:01:32.080 --> 00:01:33.600
{\an8}How could a baby
just disappear like that, Ith?

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:35.880
{\an8}Or could Donut have been kidnapped?

00:01:52.880 --> 00:01:54.840
You go that way, I'll go this way.

00:03:12.280 --> 00:03:13.400
Did you find him, Ing?

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:15.600
No.

00:03:16.280 --> 00:03:18.000
How much longer
is he going to mess with us?

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.800
He's not even picking up.

00:03:22.840 --> 00:03:23.840
Let's call the police.

00:03:28.160 --> 00:03:30.560
Donut… Donut.

00:03:31.240 --> 00:03:32.640
Donut.

00:03:40.280 --> 00:03:43.640
Donut, Mama's here. I'm here now.

00:03:44.760 --> 00:03:47.600
I'm right here, okay?

00:04:00.320 --> 00:04:02.160
How could you abandon Donut like this?

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:04.600
Do you have any humanity left?

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:06.960
It was just a moment. No big deal.

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:09.160
Our son is safe and sound.

00:04:09.760 --> 00:04:11.960
What if something had happened to him?

00:04:12.040 --> 00:04:16.240
If something was going to happen, it would
have already. Stop whining. So annoying.

00:04:17.079 --> 00:04:18.600
What do you want? Just say it.

00:04:19.200 --> 00:04:20.200
You already know.

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:23.560
I need money urgently.

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:27.800
Can you give me 200,000 in advance?

00:04:27.880 --> 00:04:31.080
You shouldn't have been a father at all.

00:04:31.160 --> 00:04:32.600
Shouldn't even have been born.

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:36.560
Stop lecturing me. Transfer the money.

00:04:37.640 --> 00:04:39.400
If you don't, next time,

00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:43.000
I can't guarantee our son's safety.

00:04:47.160 --> 00:04:51.000
I saw you left him at home and went
on a trip with your rich girlfriend.

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:54.000
Do you expect me to believe
you don't have money?

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:56.960
I can transfer 20,000 right now.

00:04:57.040 --> 00:04:58.200
Do you want it or not?

00:04:58.880 --> 00:05:00.160
Of course I want it.

00:05:02.240 --> 00:05:05.440
And don't forget the rest. Muah.

00:05:11.440 --> 00:05:12.840
What kind of man is he?

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:15.800
- So damn shameless.
- Donut.

00:05:27.760 --> 00:05:31.360
I called Ms. Lin's dad
and told him you resigned.

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:34.720
He got worried and wanted to give you
some money to help you get started.

00:05:34.800 --> 00:05:36.840
I didn't think it was a problem,

00:05:36.920 --> 00:05:38.840
so I accepted it
and transferred it to you.

00:05:38.920 --> 00:05:41.320
What would Ms. Lin think
if she knew about this?

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:43.320
I have to go.

00:05:45.880 --> 00:05:46.880
Wait, Ing.

00:05:47.400 --> 00:05:49.360
Did he really transfer it?

00:05:49.440 --> 00:05:52.560
Five hundred thousand?
He didn't send it by mistake, did he?

00:05:53.640 --> 00:05:55.840
So we don't have to
sell the car anymore, right?

00:05:56.440 --> 00:05:57.520
Yeah, I'll be right back.

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:58.920
Where are you going?

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:00.920
Take care of Donut.

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:03.280
I'll be back, okay? I'll be back soon.

00:06:08.360 --> 00:06:11.000
If you were in trouble,
why didn't you tell me?

00:06:13.280 --> 00:06:16.640
You went to see my dad without telling me.

00:06:19.600 --> 00:06:20.680
I…

00:06:23.120 --> 00:06:24.680
I didn't want to make you worry.

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:28.760
So you chose to side with him?
To betray me?

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:32.160
You took on so much work
that I barely saw you.

00:06:32.240 --> 00:06:34.400
Then suddenly,
you agreed to go to the seminar.

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:38.080
So you made it easy
for Dad to shut down Play Park.

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:43.080
And you even got 500,000 baht for free.

00:06:44.240 --> 00:06:46.480
Can you please reassure me

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:49.640
that I didn't give my heart to a liar?

00:06:58.720 --> 00:07:00.160
I made a mistake.

00:07:00.960 --> 00:07:03.120
You're not even going to explain?

00:07:07.200 --> 00:07:08.760
That's all I can say.

00:07:09.880 --> 00:07:13.480
You probably can't even come up with
a good excuse, can you?

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:31.200
Sir.

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:40.640
Please take your money back.

00:09:08.760 --> 00:09:11.000
Can you please reassure me

00:09:11.880 --> 00:09:14.160
that I didn't give my heart to a liar?

00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:16.440
I made a mistake.

00:09:17.240 --> 00:09:19.400
You're not even going to explain?

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:21.840
That's all I can say.

00:09:27.720 --> 00:09:31.600
"I'm working. Miss you so much."

00:09:31.680 --> 00:09:32.880
Let's send a selfie.

00:09:36.760 --> 00:09:38.080
Ms. Jane.

00:09:38.160 --> 00:09:40.480
The woman who came the other day
is here again.

00:09:40.560 --> 00:09:41.440
Who?

00:09:41.520 --> 00:09:44.160
The cute one with short hair.

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:46.280
Short hair?

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:50.520
- IngIng?
- Yes, that's her.

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:52.280
Uh…

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:03.040
What is it, Jane?

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:06.040
Where are you, Ms. Lin?
Please come home right now.

00:10:07.200 --> 00:10:09.440
What happened? I'm right outside.

00:10:10.200 --> 00:10:11.520
It's IngIng.

00:10:12.360 --> 00:10:14.280
You wanted Mr. Pao to fire me

00:10:15.240 --> 00:10:18.880
because I was the reason
Ms. Lin refused to close Play Park.

00:10:19.800 --> 00:10:21.440
But you didn't tell him directly.

00:10:22.520 --> 00:10:24.160
Yes, so what?

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:27.680
Don't worry about me being unemployed.

00:10:28.280 --> 00:10:31.800
I've already told Mr. Pao
that if I couldn't help Ms. Lin,

00:10:32.400 --> 00:10:34.000
I'd find another job.

00:10:34.800 --> 00:10:36.920
But I don't want
any financial help from you.

00:10:37.520 --> 00:10:39.000
You're quite clever.

00:10:41.960 --> 00:10:45.320
IngIng knew nothing
about that 500,000 baht.

00:10:45.400 --> 00:10:48.040
Your father only told you half the truth.

00:10:52.400 --> 00:10:57.440
Mr. Pao called him to say IngIng quit on
her own. She didn't want to cause trouble.

00:10:57.960 --> 00:11:02.320
So your father had me transfer
the support money through Mr. Pao.

00:11:02.840 --> 00:11:04.760
Why didn't you tell me?

00:11:04.840 --> 00:11:06.760
They were deceiving you, Ms. Lin.

00:11:06.840 --> 00:11:09.000
No one was deceiving me.

00:11:09.520 --> 00:11:11.640
Tell me the truth, Jane.

00:11:11.720 --> 00:11:13.800
What did IngIng
talk to my dad about that day?

00:11:18.680 --> 00:11:19.720
What do you want?

00:11:20.840 --> 00:11:23.520
I have something
I'd like to negotiate with you.

00:11:24.160 --> 00:11:27.920
Ms. IngIng, you should know your place.

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:32.280
What do you want
to negotiate with me about?

00:11:33.320 --> 00:11:34.440
Well…

00:11:35.320 --> 00:11:36.760
I'd like to ask for a chance

00:11:37.720 --> 00:11:40.120
for Ms. Lin to carry out her plan.

00:11:41.000 --> 00:11:43.840
Hasn't it been delayed long enough?

00:11:43.920 --> 00:11:48.080
What if I can bring in
more than half the customers?

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:50.200
Would that still be too slow?

00:11:52.360 --> 00:11:55.120
And you're confident you can do that?

00:11:55.720 --> 00:11:57.880
How much time are you asking for?

00:12:21.560 --> 00:12:23.160
You broke your promise.

00:12:24.440 --> 00:12:25.760
You used me.

00:12:26.800 --> 00:12:29.480
How dare you speak to me like that?

00:12:31.120 --> 00:12:35.040
I lied to you
because I wanted to help my daughter.

00:12:35.840 --> 00:12:37.800
If you were truly sincere with Lin,

00:12:37.880 --> 00:12:40.280
you should have helped me
from the beginning.

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:44.720
What I'm doing now is helping her too.

00:12:45.760 --> 00:12:47.080
But it's too late.

00:12:47.600 --> 00:12:49.400
Right now, her aunt has secured contracts

00:12:49.480 --> 00:12:52.760
to produce uniforms
for multiple kindergartens and nurseries.

00:12:52.840 --> 00:12:56.040
And she's about to acquire
even more factories.

00:12:56.680 --> 00:12:57.720
Meanwhile,

00:12:58.320 --> 00:13:00.360
Lin hasn't made any progress.

00:13:00.440 --> 00:13:02.680
Let me be clear.

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:06.440
Lin has been able to manage projects

00:13:06.520 --> 00:13:08.280
because of my influence.

00:13:08.920 --> 00:13:11.560
Back then, her aunt
hadn't achieved anything yet.

00:13:12.080 --> 00:13:13.880
But that's no longer the case.

00:13:14.400 --> 00:13:17.120
And the management election is coming.

00:13:17.200 --> 00:13:19.800
If this continues,
Lin will lose her position.

00:13:19.880 --> 00:13:21.600
Is that what you want?

00:13:26.480 --> 00:13:28.680
What if I withdraw
from competing against Auntie?

00:13:30.800 --> 00:13:34.000
That means we lose our chance.
Is that what you want?

00:13:34.080 --> 00:13:35.800
Are you out of your mind?

00:13:35.880 --> 00:13:39.240
I never wanted to be CEO.
I did all this for you.

00:13:40.440 --> 00:13:42.600
Let's meet halfway.

00:13:42.680 --> 00:13:45.080
Let me follow my plan,

00:13:45.160 --> 00:13:47.440
and I'll run against Auntie.

00:13:50.320 --> 00:13:53.000
I'll support Ms. Lin too.

00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:26.280
Ms. Lin.

00:14:41.240 --> 00:14:43.240
I know everything now.

00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:46.400
I'm sorry
if anything I said or did hurt you.

00:14:46.480 --> 00:14:47.920
It's okay.

00:14:48.760 --> 00:14:50.520
You didn't know, so you're not at fault.

00:14:56.280 --> 00:15:00.120
I apologize on Dad's behalf too.
Please don't be upset with him.

00:15:01.160 --> 00:15:02.400
I'm not.

00:15:03.520 --> 00:15:05.600
He did it with good intentions.

00:15:06.560 --> 00:15:10.120
We both acted for the people we love.

00:15:10.720 --> 00:15:12.400
You really know how to talk, don't you?

00:15:17.560 --> 00:15:19.040
I mean it.

00:15:19.680 --> 00:15:21.600
Then why did you resign?

00:15:23.160 --> 00:15:24.360
Well,

00:15:24.880 --> 00:15:27.880
I was afraid I wouldn't be able
to fully support your work,

00:15:28.400 --> 00:15:30.440
and I'd regret it later.

00:15:30.960 --> 00:15:34.360
And about Guy,
why didn't you talk to me first?

00:15:34.440 --> 00:15:36.280
You made me feel terrible.

00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:40.480
You already had enough stress from work.

00:15:41.400 --> 00:15:44.240
I can handle my own personal matters.

00:15:46.640 --> 00:15:49.920
So I'm still an outsider to you.

00:15:53.400 --> 00:15:55.800
Why are you sulking, huh?

00:15:55.880 --> 00:15:58.120
Then you have to let me help.

00:16:01.440 --> 00:16:02.640
No more refusing.

00:16:33.200 --> 00:16:35.040
You managed to get the money
faster than I expected.

00:16:35.840 --> 00:16:37.000
Even before the deadline.

00:16:37.600 --> 00:16:39.720
Actually,
we should've met at the district office.

00:16:41.520 --> 00:16:43.920
I've changed my mind.

00:16:44.760 --> 00:16:47.320
I'm not transferring the 500,000.
I might get scammed.

00:16:48.600 --> 00:16:50.440
Scammed? What are you talking about?

00:16:50.520 --> 00:16:52.240
I fully intend to sign.

00:16:53.040 --> 00:16:56.240
An agreement
that I won't contact either of you

00:16:56.320 --> 00:16:58.640
and won't reveal I'm the father.

00:16:59.680 --> 00:17:00.960
Tit for tat.

00:17:02.200 --> 00:17:05.079
If you don't trust me, you can sign first.
Transfer the money later.

00:17:05.680 --> 00:17:07.000
Actually, you can come see Donut.

00:17:07.079 --> 00:17:09.599
I'll even let you take him.
Do you want that?

00:17:09.680 --> 00:17:10.560
Hey, wait.

00:17:11.079 --> 00:17:12.839
Are you trying to back out on me?

00:17:14.400 --> 00:17:15.599
Fine.

00:17:17.599 --> 00:17:19.040
You'll regret this.

00:17:20.280 --> 00:17:21.880
Who's really going to regret it?

00:17:24.319 --> 00:17:26.520
LILIN

00:17:26.599 --> 00:17:27.839
What are you going to do?

00:17:34.200 --> 00:17:36.560
I recorded the entire conversation.

00:17:38.800 --> 00:17:42.440
A post-divorce agreement to give up
visitation rights and deny paternity,

00:17:42.520 --> 00:17:45.880
that's not legally valid,

00:17:47.400 --> 00:17:48.720
is it, counselor?

00:17:48.800 --> 00:17:53.200
Yes, and it also
concerns the child's rights.

00:17:53.880 --> 00:17:55.520
You already knew

00:17:55.600 --> 00:17:57.080
and you were planning to deceive me?

00:17:57.160 --> 00:17:58.440
I don't know.

00:17:59.520 --> 00:18:01.080
I really intended to sign it for you.

00:18:01.160 --> 00:18:03.280
And do you realize that what you did,

00:18:03.360 --> 00:18:06.440
extorting money, breaking into the house,
and taking Donut away,

00:18:06.520 --> 00:18:08.200
is illegal?

00:18:09.560 --> 00:18:11.560
There are multiple charges.

00:18:11.640 --> 00:18:15.920
Extortion, trespassing, and kidnapping.

00:18:16.000 --> 00:18:17.960
The penalties include
both imprisonment and fines.

00:18:19.880 --> 00:18:22.640
I have evidence, video and audio,

00:18:23.560 --> 00:18:25.160
the transfer receipt,

00:18:25.680 --> 00:18:28.920
surveillance footage
from the park that day,

00:18:29.000 --> 00:18:31.680
and from today as well.

00:18:35.840 --> 00:18:37.520
Ms. IngIng, I suggest

00:18:37.600 --> 00:18:40.680
you file a police report
to keep as evidence.

00:18:41.200 --> 00:18:42.040
Yes.

00:18:42.640 --> 00:18:43.560
A police report?

00:18:47.360 --> 00:18:48.400
I'm sorry.

00:18:49.160 --> 00:18:50.200
I'm sorry, IngIng.

00:18:50.800 --> 00:18:52.160
I won't do it again.

00:18:52.240 --> 00:18:54.400
I promise I won't bother you anymore.

00:18:55.640 --> 00:18:57.000
Please don't report me.

00:18:57.680 --> 00:18:59.080
If you break your promise,

00:18:59.600 --> 00:19:01.600
I'll submit all the evidence
and file the report.

00:19:04.600 --> 00:19:05.680
I won't break it.

00:19:06.960 --> 00:19:07.800
Thank you.

00:19:08.800 --> 00:19:09.880
If there's nothing else,

00:19:09.960 --> 00:19:11.440
- I'll be going now.
- Wait.

00:19:13.280 --> 00:19:15.120
Transfer me 20,000 baht as well.

00:19:15.880 --> 00:19:18.160
We've run out of money
for Donut's milk and diapers.

00:19:18.240 --> 00:19:19.240
Huh?

00:19:21.600 --> 00:19:22.600
Yeah.

00:19:23.640 --> 00:19:24.840
I'll transfer it.

00:19:32.200 --> 00:19:33.240
That's all, right?

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:34.960
You can go now.

00:19:43.800 --> 00:19:45.000
Thank you.

00:19:45.520 --> 00:19:46.560
You're welcome.

00:19:52.080 --> 00:19:53.200
You did great.

00:20:04.160 --> 00:20:06.600
{\an8}DEAR CUSTOMERS
PLAY PARK IS TEMPORARY CLOSED

00:20:10.560 --> 00:20:11.800
Come on!

00:20:14.600 --> 00:20:18.160
- Yay!
- Yeah!

00:20:59.040 --> 00:21:00.840
I've got a new idea.

00:21:00.920 --> 00:21:03.080
I don't think
we should close Play Park anymore.

00:21:03.160 --> 00:21:04.480
Why not?

00:21:04.560 --> 00:21:07.640
I've been observing
the tutoring booths we set up.

00:21:08.360 --> 00:21:12.120
Letting kids play and learn
at the same time seems to work better.

00:21:13.360 --> 00:21:16.520
They look happy,
and they actually enjoy learning.

00:21:17.040 --> 00:21:18.440
So…

00:21:19.680 --> 00:21:21.640
where would the classrooms be?

00:21:21.720 --> 00:21:24.840
We can repurpose some parts of the park.

00:21:33.760 --> 00:21:36.880
I'm just building on your idea.

00:21:37.640 --> 00:21:39.840
I also did some research.

00:21:40.360 --> 00:21:42.160
A lot of studies show

00:21:42.240 --> 00:21:46.120
that happy kids learn better
than stressed ones.

00:21:47.760 --> 00:21:52.400
So we need to make them happy,
make them enjoy coming here to study.

00:21:52.480 --> 00:21:53.840
And…

00:21:54.920 --> 00:21:56.480
your dad won't have a problem with that?

00:21:57.080 --> 00:21:58.680
We don't have to tell him yet.

00:21:59.400 --> 00:22:02.040
For something like this,
you prove it through results.

00:22:05.160 --> 00:22:07.760
My girlfriend is really smart.

00:22:13.520 --> 00:22:14.640
So smart.

00:22:38.160 --> 00:22:41.120
Kids, listen up for a moment.

00:22:41.200 --> 00:22:45.200
You'll study for one hour, then I'll come
get you so you can go play, okay?

00:22:45.280 --> 00:22:47.120
- Okay.
- Okay.

00:22:47.200 --> 00:22:50.440
Awesome. You guys are the best.

00:22:50.960 --> 00:22:54.120
- Let's study. Listen to your teacher.
- Yes.

00:22:55.760 --> 00:22:58.400
Wow, what a cute fish!

00:22:59.400 --> 00:23:01.520
A pink fish?

00:23:02.320 --> 00:23:05.120
Focus on your lesson first.
I'll come get you later, okay?

00:23:05.200 --> 00:23:06.160
Alright?

00:23:12.880 --> 00:23:16.000
Sir, IngIng has sent
the list of customers.

00:23:16.080 --> 00:23:17.600
Both classes are fully booked now.

00:23:20.000 --> 00:23:22.400
LITTLE JOY SCHOOL
CLASS 1 REGISTRATION LIST

00:23:24.280 --> 00:23:27.320
I think we'll need to expand
the classrooms.

00:23:27.920 --> 00:23:29.680
You're really good
at talking them up, huh?

00:23:31.120 --> 00:23:32.080
Oh.

00:23:48.800 --> 00:23:50.040
You see that?

00:23:50.120 --> 00:23:51.440
- Want the crocodile?
- Crocodile?

00:23:51.960 --> 00:23:53.360
- You want it?
- Yeah?

00:23:53.440 --> 00:23:54.520
Whoa.

00:23:55.640 --> 00:23:58.160
You're nibbling on the crocodile again.

00:23:58.680 --> 00:24:00.520
- Ing! Ing!
- What?

00:24:00.600 --> 00:24:01.520
Let me kiss your cheek.

00:24:04.720 --> 00:24:05.560
What?

00:24:05.640 --> 00:24:07.440
I passed the interview.

00:24:07.520 --> 00:24:09.160
- Really?
- Yeah.

00:24:10.080 --> 00:24:12.240
They want me to start next week.

00:24:12.320 --> 00:24:14.840
Yeah? That's great.

00:24:15.760 --> 00:24:17.040
I'm happy for you, Ith.

00:24:17.640 --> 00:24:18.560
Thank you.

00:24:18.640 --> 00:24:21.280
Let's celebrate, yay!

00:24:22.080 --> 00:24:23.400
Uh, well…

00:24:24.000 --> 00:24:25.600
who's going to look after Donut?

00:24:26.360 --> 00:24:27.480
It's okay.

00:24:27.560 --> 00:24:30.480
I can afford daycare now.
Don't worry about it.

00:24:32.680 --> 00:24:35.720
Maybe we won't
even have to send him to daycare.

00:24:37.480 --> 00:24:38.760
What do you mean?

00:24:38.840 --> 00:24:40.440
Then who's going to look after him?

00:24:42.840 --> 00:24:43.760
Hm?

00:24:48.840 --> 00:24:51.520
During the day,
no one is at IngIng's house.

00:24:52.040 --> 00:24:54.480
I've kept her busy with work.

00:24:54.560 --> 00:24:58.160
I didn't want to worry about the kid,
so I brought him to stay with us.

00:24:59.040 --> 00:25:02.000
I haven't been able to find
a daycare I like yet.

00:25:02.080 --> 00:25:03.240
It's quite urgent.

00:25:05.320 --> 00:25:08.040
But if Ms. Lin hired a nanny to help out,

00:25:08.120 --> 00:25:09.720
there shouldn't be
any problems, right, sir?

00:25:11.800 --> 00:25:13.720
You won't mind a child, will you, sir?

00:25:16.400 --> 00:25:18.640
No. The house is big enough.

00:25:18.720 --> 00:25:20.640
Thank you very much.

00:25:22.400 --> 00:25:25.440
If everything is settled,
let's get to work.

00:25:25.520 --> 00:25:26.520
Right.

00:25:27.040 --> 00:25:28.040
Come on.

00:25:28.120 --> 00:25:31.000
Stay with Grandpa for now.
I'll come pick you up in the evening.

00:25:32.600 --> 00:25:33.480
We're heading off.

00:25:40.920 --> 00:25:42.000
Mama's going to work.

00:25:42.600 --> 00:25:43.800
Bye-bye.

00:25:44.800 --> 00:25:46.120
Bye-bye.

00:25:46.720 --> 00:25:48.160
I'm off to work now.

00:25:51.880 --> 00:25:53.000
Bye-bye. Bye-bye.

00:25:53.600 --> 00:25:54.720
Bye-bye.

00:25:55.360 --> 00:25:56.480
Bye-bye.

00:26:12.680 --> 00:26:14.120
And what about the father?

00:26:14.200 --> 00:26:18.200
Divorced a long time ago. He abandoned him
at birth and has never taken care of him.

00:26:19.400 --> 00:26:20.840
So she's a single mom, huh?

00:26:20.920 --> 00:26:22.200
Yes, sir.

00:26:50.640 --> 00:26:53.160
Oh, wow.

00:26:53.240 --> 00:26:56.040
Oppa! Look at Uncle Ith.

00:26:56.120 --> 00:26:57.320
Shut up.

00:26:57.960 --> 00:26:59.920
I'm not used to this at all.

00:27:00.000 --> 00:27:03.200
You look more like a grown-up now.
What do you mean you're not used to it?

00:27:03.280 --> 00:27:05.560
Go on, hurry up and get to work.
You'll be late.

00:27:06.480 --> 00:27:07.400
Okay.

00:27:07.480 --> 00:27:08.400
Mm.

00:27:08.480 --> 00:27:10.760
I'm going now.

00:27:10.840 --> 00:27:13.040
Bye-bye, Uncle Ith. Bye-bye.

00:27:13.120 --> 00:27:14.960
- Bye.
- Bye-bye.

00:27:37.240 --> 00:27:39.800
Ms. Lin, this is from your father.

00:27:43.880 --> 00:27:45.400
I'll go greet the guests now.

00:27:50.480 --> 00:27:53.480
MY BRILLIANT GIRL

00:28:39.480 --> 00:28:41.040
Nom, nom, nom.

00:28:42.600 --> 00:28:45.880
Nom, nom, nom.

00:28:45.960 --> 00:28:47.200
Nom, nom.

00:28:48.120 --> 00:28:49.280
Here.

00:28:50.760 --> 00:28:53.080
I brought the dog for you.

00:28:53.760 --> 00:28:54.880
Do you like it?

00:28:56.200 --> 00:28:58.280
Look at the dog. See?

00:29:09.400 --> 00:29:10.800
I'll keep it for you.

00:29:12.200 --> 00:29:13.360
Play with the crocodile.

00:29:54.240 --> 00:29:55.840
Dad's smitten with his grandson.

00:29:57.080 --> 00:29:58.880
I told you he's such a well-behaved child

00:30:00.480 --> 00:30:04.120
You're cunning, finding a way
to win over your girlfriend's father.

00:30:04.200 --> 00:30:07.480
Who came up with that idea first?

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:18.240
Actually, Donut can stay over sometimes
if you two finish work late.

00:30:18.320 --> 00:30:20.000
So he won't have to travel too much.

00:30:20.520 --> 00:30:23.360
There are plenty of rooms here.
He can even stay in your old room.

00:30:23.440 --> 00:30:26.160
Well, his mom and uncle
would miss him so much.

00:30:26.760 --> 00:30:30.320
He doesn't need to stay over every day.
Just on nights when you finish work late.

00:30:32.480 --> 00:30:35.080
If Donut's grandpa doesn't mind,

00:30:35.160 --> 00:30:36.440
that would be great.

00:30:37.120 --> 00:30:38.320
Thank you so much.

00:30:41.240 --> 00:30:45.560
If I get appointed CEO,
can I invite Ing to stay at my house too?

00:30:46.520 --> 00:30:50.040
That way, Donut won't have to commute.
I'd feel bad for him.

00:30:51.920 --> 00:30:54.200
You've become quite tricky these days.

00:30:57.000 --> 00:30:58.360
Thank you, Dad.

00:31:22.000 --> 00:31:23.120
Hmm.

00:31:24.960 --> 00:31:27.000
I'll kiss you back.

00:31:29.560 --> 00:31:31.360
- Babe.
- Hm?

00:31:33.040 --> 00:31:34.920
What did you say just now?

00:31:35.000 --> 00:31:36.360
Nothing.

00:31:36.440 --> 00:31:37.440
Hm?

00:31:38.240 --> 00:31:40.400
But I heard you just now.

00:31:42.120 --> 00:31:42.960
Here.

00:31:43.720 --> 00:31:46.400
Our classes are fully booked now.
Are you happy?

00:31:46.920 --> 00:31:48.480
Should we open more branches?

00:31:48.560 --> 00:31:52.000
Take it easy.
There's no need to rush at all.

00:31:53.440 --> 00:31:56.640
I guess the CEO position
is pretty much in the bag now, huh?

00:31:58.200 --> 00:31:59.680
I'm nervous about it too.

00:32:00.200 --> 00:32:02.720
Don't worry about a thing.

00:32:02.800 --> 00:32:06.040
There's really nothing to worry about.
We've done our best.

00:32:06.120 --> 00:32:08.480
And even if we do make a mistake,

00:32:09.000 --> 00:32:10.360
your dad won't mind.

00:32:11.440 --> 00:32:14.440
Having a new daughter-in-law
and grandson should make up for it.

00:32:18.560 --> 00:32:20.640
You're old news now.

00:32:20.720 --> 00:32:22.080
Do you realize that?

00:32:22.640 --> 00:32:23.680
Right?

00:32:26.720 --> 00:32:27.880
Shall we go for a walk?

00:32:27.960 --> 00:32:29.680
Mm, let's go.

00:32:36.400 --> 00:32:38.120
- Come on.
- Let's go.

00:32:45.400 --> 00:32:48.320
My tutoring school
really took off thanks to you, Ing.

00:32:49.400 --> 00:32:51.440
It's because we helped each other.

00:32:53.080 --> 00:32:57.360
I'm so lucky. It's like unboxing
a blind box and finding the secret figure.

00:32:58.480 --> 00:32:59.400
The secret figure?

00:33:01.400 --> 00:33:02.720
I'm serious.

00:33:03.320 --> 00:33:07.680
My work is progressing,
and my dad has accepted my relationship.

00:33:09.400 --> 00:33:10.800
It's all because of you, Ing.

00:33:14.920 --> 00:33:17.640
I feel like
I'm the luckiest person in the world.

00:33:19.080 --> 00:33:21.360
This year has been the best year for me.

00:33:59.760 --> 00:34:02.960
Okay, you look beautiful
and ready to win the vote.

00:34:03.040 --> 00:34:04.680
I'm so nervous.

00:34:06.560 --> 00:34:08.840
Okay, take a deep breath in.

00:34:09.880 --> 00:34:11.000
And breathe out slowly.

00:34:13.400 --> 00:34:14.679
Great job.

00:34:15.600 --> 00:34:17.159
And remember,

00:34:17.239 --> 00:34:21.159
we've done our best.
If we don't get it, it's okay, right?

00:34:23.639 --> 00:34:24.679
Hm.

00:34:38.040 --> 00:34:40.520
Ms. Lin, everyone is at the meeting now.

00:34:42.040 --> 00:34:44.000
Okay. Uh…

00:34:44.080 --> 00:34:45.880
I'll wait outside.

00:34:50.239 --> 00:34:51.159
Are you ready?

00:34:52.520 --> 00:34:54.360
Okay, stand up

00:34:55.679 --> 00:34:56.600
Listen.

00:34:57.880 --> 00:34:59.320
I'll cheer you on.

00:35:56.920 --> 00:35:59.920
Well, what's next?
How should we conclude this?

00:36:08.280 --> 00:36:09.560
Then,

00:36:10.320 --> 00:36:11.640
I'd like to choose…

00:36:19.320 --> 00:36:21.480
- Don't be nervous, Ms. Ing.
- I am right now.

00:36:21.560 --> 00:36:23.280
Oh, I think I'm going to pass out.

00:36:23.360 --> 00:36:24.200
Oh?

00:36:32.240 --> 00:36:34.400
Please give a round of applause
to my talented niece.

00:36:36.800 --> 00:36:37.920
Ms. Lin!

00:36:56.840 --> 00:36:58.720
Give her a big hand please.

00:37:01.920 --> 00:37:03.040
Congratulations.

00:37:14.920 --> 00:37:16.480
Come on, let me kiss your cheeks.

00:37:22.200 --> 00:37:23.040
You did a great job.

00:37:24.160 --> 00:37:25.840
You played a really important role.

00:37:26.840 --> 00:37:27.960
Mm.

00:37:29.440 --> 00:37:31.920
You know, when your aunt came out,

00:37:32.000 --> 00:37:34.440
I was almost in shock.
I was completely surprised.

00:37:36.360 --> 00:37:38.080
I didn't expect it either.

00:37:39.040 --> 00:37:40.760
She probably did it to please Dad.

00:37:41.800 --> 00:37:42.880
Mm.

00:37:44.000 --> 00:37:45.480
Let me kiss you again.

00:37:57.520 --> 00:38:00.080
I'm on my way home,
so I just stopped by to see you first.

00:38:13.640 --> 00:38:14.680
Great job, dear.

00:38:25.520 --> 00:38:28.320
Please keep helping Lin with her work.
Don't abandon each other.

00:38:30.200 --> 00:38:31.120
Yes.

00:38:36.560 --> 00:38:38.080
I'm leaving now.

00:38:40.800 --> 00:38:42.120
Dad.

00:38:54.680 --> 00:38:55.880
Thank you.

00:39:31.160 --> 00:39:32.040
Are you happy?

00:39:42.960 --> 00:39:45.320
What's the occasion for the movie date?

00:39:47.240 --> 00:39:49.640
This is our first time
watching a movie at the theater.

00:39:57.920 --> 00:39:58.920
Ing,

00:40:00.320 --> 00:40:04.240
I never thought I would meet someone
who would make my life like this.

00:40:11.960 --> 00:40:14.600
Thank you for always being by my side.

00:40:18.120 --> 00:40:19.840
I want to take care of you.

00:40:24.680 --> 00:40:28.080
I want to see Donut grow up along with us.

00:40:32.720 --> 00:40:35.720
And I also want Ith, your little brother,

00:40:35.800 --> 00:40:37.960
to be my little brother too.

00:40:46.280 --> 00:40:47.800
Will you marry me?

00:41:34.560 --> 00:41:35.560
Yes.

00:41:59.280 --> 00:42:03.400
- I first met you here.
- And you fell in love right away?

00:42:04.120 --> 00:42:05.280
That's too sudden.

00:42:05.360 --> 00:42:07.200
Hm, then

00:42:07.280 --> 00:42:09.920
you were attracted to me
from the first time you saw me?

00:42:10.600 --> 00:42:12.080
Of course.

00:42:16.240 --> 00:42:19.720
So when did you fall in love with me, Ing?

00:42:21.320 --> 00:42:23.520
I don't know. I won't tell you.

00:42:24.400 --> 00:42:28.120
I can guess, and I remember the date too.

00:42:29.200 --> 00:42:31.880
What are you thinking about? Tell me.

00:42:31.960 --> 00:42:33.920
I don't know. I won't tell you.

00:43:56.680 --> 00:43:57.800
Again?

00:43:58.520 --> 00:43:59.440
Hm?

00:44:00.640 --> 00:44:03.200
Look over there. Do you see any birds?

00:44:10.800 --> 00:44:12.280
Wow.

00:44:12.360 --> 00:44:14.720
What a handsome boy.

00:44:14.800 --> 00:44:16.240
What's your name?

00:44:16.920 --> 00:44:17.920
His name is Donut.

00:44:19.560 --> 00:44:20.680
Donut?

00:44:24.280 --> 00:44:25.440
Congratulations.

00:44:31.200 --> 00:44:34.680
My boss went to your wedding.
That's how I saw your photos.

00:44:35.360 --> 00:44:36.280
Oh.

00:44:36.360 --> 00:44:37.320
Thank you.

00:44:38.080 --> 00:44:40.160
Your wedding was so lovely.

00:44:40.240 --> 00:44:43.360
We're also looking for ideas
for our own wedding.

00:44:45.840 --> 00:44:47.600
Congratulations in advance.

00:44:48.640 --> 00:44:49.720
Thank you.

00:44:52.400 --> 00:44:54.120
We won't bother you anymore, then.

00:44:54.720 --> 00:44:55.760
Right.

00:44:55.840 --> 00:44:57.440
- Say bye to the beautiful ladies.
- Bye-bye.

00:44:57.520 --> 00:44:58.960
- Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

00:44:59.040 --> 00:45:00.640
- Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

00:45:00.720 --> 00:45:02.160
- Bye-bye.
- Good boy.

00:45:03.760 --> 00:45:05.000
We'll get going now.

00:45:05.520 --> 00:45:06.640
Please feel free.

00:45:06.720 --> 00:45:08.800
That's enough, Donut. They're leaving.

00:45:11.400 --> 00:45:12.440
Cute, right?

00:45:13.960 --> 00:45:15.280
The baby or the adults?

00:45:17.200 --> 00:45:19.920
The baby, of course.
You're picking a fight again.

00:45:21.560 --> 00:45:22.520
- Let's go.
- Uh-huh.

00:45:23.040 --> 00:45:25.040
- Don't let me catch you.
- Come on.

00:45:42.880 --> 00:45:43.920
I love you.

00:45:45.960 --> 00:45:47.240
I love you.

00:48:39.840 --> 00:48:42.200
Subtitle translation by:
Anan Pratchayakul